	 <DL> 
		<DT><FONT SIZE="+1">KADMOS Help File for Irfanview</FONT></DT> 
		<DD>Die Bediener-Sprache ist in Irfanview unter Options,
		  Properties/Settings, Languages einzustellen. <BR>User language setting has to
		  be done in Irfanview under Options, Properties/Settings, Languages.<BR> <BR>If
		  an image has been loaded with Irfanview and the Kadmos character recognition
		  has been started, a new window opens with the loaded imgage on the left side.
		  <BR><BR>Character recognition is started by a mouse click at one of the yellow
		  marked text areas or by marking any other area with mouse and rubber band. An
		  edit window with the recognition result opens up. Here the result can be edited
		  or stored. <BR><BR><BR></DD> 
		<DT><FONT SIZE="+1">Configuration: </FONT></DT> 
		<DD> Here parameters fo character recognition can be set, as for instance
		  character height, line pitch, or method of noise reduction. Also the character
		  set of the loaded classifier can be resticted. <BR><BR><BR></DD> 
		<DT><FONT SIZE="+1">Select OCR language: </FONT></DT> 
		<DD>Before character recognition can be started, the OCR language has to
		  be selected. With a click on the arrow in the selection window all installed
		  languages are listed. If the wanted language is not contained, then click on
		  &quot;Download more languages&quot; .<BR><BR><BR></DD> 
		<DT><FONT SIZE="+1">Download more OCR languages: </FONT> </DT> 
		<DD>A window &quot;Download KADMOS classifier&quot; opens. With a click on the
		  arrow of the selection window all selectable languages are listed.</DD> 
	 </DL> </BODY>
